odes and analyze them with CCME, yielding results that reveal\nmacro-features of the corresponding systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 13:44:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 Jan 2016 17:51:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2017 19:51:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 23 Oct 2017 07:39:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-24"}
