covariant\nparametrizations of Lambda term like $\\Lambda(a)$, $\\Lambda(H)$ give rise to\npathological and nonphysical behaviour of trajectories in the phase space. This\nbehaviour disappears if the term $\\Lambda(a)$ is emergent from the covariant\nparametrization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 15:05:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-29"}
